# ORAS Python [![All Contributors](https://img.shields.io/badge/all_contributors-20-orange.svg?style=flat-square)](#contributors-) ![ORAS Logo](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/oras-project/oras-www/main/static/img/oras.png) OCI Registry as Storage enables libraries to push OCI Artifacts to [OCI Conformant](https://github.com/opencontainers/oci-conformance) registries. This is a Python SDK for Python developers to empower them to do this in their applications.
